/#
   The method, prioritzed by the order it is listed in this element, to get a replacement rate for the disrupted settlement rate option.
 #/
record FpML5.confirmation.FallbackReferencePrice {
  # Specifies how long to wait to get a quote from a settlement rate option upon a price source disruption
  valuationPostponement : FpML5.confirmation.ValuationPostponement?

  # This settlement rate option will be used in its place.
  fallbackSettlementRateOption : string?

  # Request rate quotes from the market.
  fallbackSurveyValuationPostponenment : FpML5.confirmation.Empty?

  # The calculation agent will decide the rate.
  calculationAgentDetermination : FpML5.confirmation.CalculationAgent?

}

valuationPostponement.Doc: Specifies how long to wait to get a quote from a settlement rate option upon a price source disruption
valuationPostponement.Name: valuationPostponement

fallbackSurveyValuationPostponenment.Name: fallbackSurveyValuationPostponenment

calculationAgentDetermination.Name: calculationAgentDetermination
